# Description:
# Digital port template. This template is used to define a pair 
# of multi bit binary records. One is an mbbiDirect record, the other an
# mbboDirect record. 
#
# This template defines a pair of mbbiDirect and mbboDirect process variables.
#
# NAME - Sector or Ioc name eg. SR12ID01 or SR12ID01IOC01
# FIELDDEV - Name of field device eg. MPS01, ADC01
# BITFUNC - The digital bit description
# BYTEFUNC - The digital byte description that the bit comes from.  
# BITNUM - bit number description, must be compatible with mbbi format eg. BO - B7
# DESC - digital bit or byte description for user

